@startuml uc-7_trace_evolution
!include ../../_theme.iuml

title UC-7 — Trace evolution

|Student|
start
:Select a species in a starter line;
|System|
:Read `species.evolution_line` and `evolution_rules`;
repeat
    :Describe next `EvolutionRule`
    (`Level`, `Item`, `Friendship`,
     `Trade`, `Location`, `TimeOfDay`,
     or `CompositeEvolutionRule`);
repeat while (more stages?) is (yes) not (no)
|Student|
:Focus the Evolution tab;
|System|
:Render ordered stages + short rule descriptions;
|Student|
if (Select an instance instead?) then (yes)
    :Re-select to see `can_evolve_now`;
    |System|
    :Evaluate rules against level / friendship;
endif
stop

@enduml
